# 三、Architecture Goals

建立：

- One Enterprise Gateway
- One Integration Runtime
- One Canonical Contract
- One Enterprise Event Bus
- One Enterprise Capability Fabric
- One Enterprise Connector Platform

形成：

Enterprise Integration Platform（EIP）。

